            <div type="transcript" id="J869">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Because the Bee may blameless hum</l>
                    <l>For Thee a Bee do I become</l>
                    <l>List even unto Me.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Because the Flowers unafraid</l>
                    <l>May lift a look on thine, a Maid</l>
                    <l>Alway a Flower would be.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Nor Robins, Robins need not hide</l>
                    <l>When Thou upon their Crypts intrude</l>
                    <l>So Wings bestow on Me</l>
                    <l>Or Petals, or a Dower of Buzz</l>
                    <l>That Bee to ride, or Flower of Furze</l>
                    <l>I that way worship Thee.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
